Name: Frequency of SW-Reviewer Declined occurring after SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' for cases where activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' occurs

Name: Percentage of process variants in which SW-Reviewer Declined appears at least once
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' out of all cases

Name: Number of times SW-Reviewer Declined is followed by another SW-AE Assign Reviewers within the same case

Name: Percentage of SW-Reviewer Declined that occur before any SW-Reviewer Agreed in a case

Name: Frequency of SW-Reviewer Declined relative to the total number of SW-AE Assign Reviewers executions

Name: Percentage of cases containing SW-Reviewer Declined that eventually reach SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' out of all 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Number of SW-Reviewer Declined occurrences per variant type

Name: Ratio of SW-Reviewer Declined to SW-Reviewer Agreed across the entire event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Percentage of cases where SW-Reviewer Declined appears more than once

Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' does not occur

Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' out of all cases
